thread.title: Sharryn Baird
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Sharryn Baird

author: Sharryn Baird
title: Sharryn Baird
text:
I couldn't be happier with my recent experience selling my property through Nelson Alexander and Jayson Watts. From my first interaction with Jayson and his team it was quite evident that I was dealing with the most professional of agents.
Throughout the preparation of my sales campaign Jayson was easy to contact, insightful, understanding and practical.
His team assisted me get our property sale ready which was a great support, and once the property hit the market couldn't have asked for more professionalism.
The property was sold the day of the first inspection which was an amazing result.
I couldn't be more pleased with my experience and highly recommend anybody looking to employ Jayson Watts to sell their property.
